A Map by Jamesknaack

This map is to record places of significance to Rosie and James

properties.name: Addis Ababa, Ethiopia
properties.description: Posted by JamesknaackLocation of Africa\'s largest outdoor market, the tomb of Ethiopia\'s first nurse and many kings and, oh yeah, the Ark of the Covenant is at nearby... (Rosie saw the city and the tombs, but not the ark!)

properties.name: Africa Renewal Ministries
properties.description: Posted by JamesknaackGaba, UgandaARM, where Rosie most recently visited Uganda and was blessed to work with for two and a half years.

properties.name: Arise Uganda Crusade
properties.description: Posted by JamesknaackGulu, UgandaArise Uganda was a crusade for Christ in Gulu. Rosie visited an IDP camp and hospital, picked up trash on the streets with the Ugandan National Soccer team, the Cranes, and prayed with hundreds of people at the crusade.
